headline: Omnicom Gears Up to Report Q2 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: OMC is set to report Q2 results on July 15, with revenues and EPS both expected to rise despite expense pressures.

headline: Veralto Schedules Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Call
summary: Veralto Corporation (NYSE: VLTO), a global leader in essential water and product quality solutions dedicated to Safeguarding the World's Most Vital Resources™, announced that it will webcast its second quarter 2025 earnings conference call on Tuesday, July 29, 2025, beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET.
